Pat Harmon https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pat_Harmon 0 Plummer Hull Harman (February 3, 1886 – November 26, 1958), known professionally as Pat Harmon, was an American film actor. He appeared in 134 films between 1920 and 1947. He was born in Lewistown, Illinois and died in Riverside, California.
